VRaptor Example 1
=================

VRaptor basic example


Install
=======

$ mvn clean install


Configure IDE Eclipse
=====================

$ mvn eclipse:clean eclipse:eclipse


Deploy
======

$ export JAVA_HOME=/path/to/java
$ export CATALINA_HOME=/path/to/apache-tomcat
$ mvn clean install cargo:deploy


References
==========

http://maven.apache.org/archetype/maven-archetype-plugin/usage.html
http://vraptor.caelum.com.br/documentation/vraptor3-ten-minutes-guide/
http://cargo.codehaus.org/Maven2+plugin


Dependecies
===========

. JDK 1.6 - http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html
. Maven 3.x - http://maven.apache.org/
. Maven plugin Cargo - http://cargo.codehaus.org/Maven2+plugin
. VRaptor 3.x - http://vraptor.caelum.com.br/


